  "prompt": "Which is the Best SEO Company in Delhi for Digital Marketing Services?",
  "response": "Choosing the best SEO company in Delhi for digital marketing services can vary based on your specific needs, budget, and industry. However, some well-regarded SEO and digital marketing agencies in Delhi as of 2023 include:\n\n1. **WebFX** - Known for its comprehensive digital marketing services, including SEO, PPC, and social media marketing.\n2. **Techmagnate** - Offers a range of digital marketing services and has a strong reputation for SEO.\n3. **iProspect India** - A part of the Dentsu Aegis Network, this agency focuses on a broad spectrum of digital marketing and has extensive experience in SEO.\n4. **PageTraffic** - Specializes in SEO and has a good track record with both local and international clients.\n5. **SEO Services Company** - Offers tailored SEO solutions and focuses on measurable results.\n\nWhen selecting an SEO company, consider factors like their case studies, client reviews, service offerings, and how well they understand your specific business goals. Always schedule consultations to discuss your needs and evaluate their proposed strategies.",
